videos.headline: Harris just short of TD on 8-yard run
videos.description: Alabama's Najee Harris extends for the goal line and comes up just short.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Harris just short of TD on 8-yard run) 2019/01/07

videos.headline: Alabama scores 1-yard TD, misses PAT
videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa finds Hale Hentges wide open in the end zone and Joseph Bulovas misses the PAT as Alabama pulls within one of Clemson.

tracking.trackingName: evc_NCF_20190107_clem_@_ala_8ac525c1-493b-4b7e-a968-a0cdea5f7d50

videos.headline: Etienne powers up the middle for Clemson TD
videos.description: Travis Etienne finds the hole and runs into the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Clemson strikes first on pick-six of Tua
videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa's pass is intercepted by A.J. Terrell, who takes it to the house for a Clemson touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clemson strikes first on pick-six of Tua) 2019/1/7 ESHEET ENHL

videos.headline: Tua, Alabama answer back with deep TD

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tua, Alabama answer back with deep TD) 2019/1/7 ESHEET ENHL
